headline: TikTok Restoring Service for U.S. Users, After Trump Signals He Will Save It
summary: The president-elect said he will issue an executive order, and the app said it will work on a long-term solution with the incoming administration.

headline: 1 BlackRock ETF to Buy Before It Soars Up to 140% in 2025, According to Certain Wall Street Analysts
summary: Bitcoin (CRYPTO: BTC) had a phenomenal year in 2024.  The cryptocurrency returned 119%, easily outperforming the 23% gain in the S&P 500 (SNPINDEX: ^GSPC), which itself is commonly seen as a barometer for the overall U.S. stock market.  Matthew Sigel, head of digital asset research at VanEck, thinks Bitcoin could hit $180,000 in 2025.
